Some tricks for slide shows based on markdown with reveal.js
------------------------------------------------------------

Fragments
---------

One element just above:
<!-- .element: class="fragment" data-fragment-index="1" -->

A whole block

<div class="fragment" data-fragment-index="1">

Text (note that the empty lines just below and above are needed)

</div>


